        "path": "/books/kitab-al-duafa:24:34:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/17/24/34/1",
        "text": [
          "34 - سليم بن قيس الهلالي. لم يرو عنه إلا أبان بن أبي عياش. وفي الكتاب مناكير مشتهرة، وما أظنه إلا موضوعا."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.tashayyu": [
            "34 – Sulaym b. Qays al-Hilālī.  No one but Abān b. Abī ʿAyyash has narrated from him.  And in his book there are notorious unrecognized (things).  And I do not deem it to be but fabricated."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  },
